{
    "typeName": "Terraform::DigitalOcean::VolumeAttachment",
    "description": "Manages attaching a Volume to a Droplet.\n\n~> **NOTE:** Volumes can be attached either directly on the `digitalocean_droplet` resource, or using the `digitalocean_volume_attachment` resource - but the two cannot be used together. If both are used against the same Droplet, the volume attachments will constantly drift.",
